320c4204fe1289d63ee700144ada0c7781067e42.query:
INSERT INTO menus (id, title, supplier, supplier_reference)
                VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4)
                ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING

32eaa3aea4c784822145e61f18db34aef40f2ac1.query:
INSERT INTO days (menu_id, date, meals)
                            VALUES ($1, $2, $3)
                            ON CONFLICT ON CONSTRAINT days_pkey DO UPDATE
                            SET meals = excluded.meals

dc05fb0c3f83d58b8cd634bec7d9b147c2e4c359.query:
INSERT INTO menus (id, title, supplier, supplier_reference, longitude, latitude)
                VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)
                ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET
                    title = excluded.title,
                    supplier = excluded.supplier,
                    supplier_reference = excluded.supplier_reference,
                    longitude = excluded.longitude,
                    latitude = excluded.latitude

dc0e4660017adc7b4855ef0d85c8b541e7546c9b.query:
UPDATE menus SET
                checked_at = $1,
                title = $2,
                longitude = $3,
                latitude = $4,
                osm_id = $5,
                consecutive_failures = CASE
                    WHEN $6 THEN 0
                    ELSE consecutive_failures + 1
                END
            WHERE id = $7
